423
00:27:11,615 --> 00:27:13,415
SIM

424
00:27:16,215 --> 00:27:17,549
BUSCA DE ESPOSAS PERSAS

425
00:27:17,549 --> 00:27:23,082
Olá, sou Faranoosh.
Será meu homem?

426
00:27:23,082 --> 00:27:25,549
Acho que sim.

427
00:27:26,482 --> 00:27:27,749
Com licença?

428
00:27:27,749 --> 00:27:30,148
Poderiam ajudar meu
novo empreendimento?

429
00:27:30,148 --> 00:27:31,081
E do que se trata?

430
00:27:31,081 --> 00:27:34,414
